---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Reveal } from '../../components/Reveal';

const title = "Transformative Breathwork — With Miro Kloosterman";
const description = "Transformative breathwork — conscious connected breathing combined with bodywork and sound. In-person or online.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="py-section-y px-section-x max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <Reveal client:load>
      <div class="mb-24">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-soil-muted mb-8 block">Session Modality</span>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display mb-12 text-soil leading-tight">Transformative Breathwork</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-soil-muted max-w-3xl mb-12 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Conscious connected breathing combined with bodywork, movement, and sound. Not breathing to feel calmer. Breathing to move what the mind can't reach on its own.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Reveal>

    <div class="space-y-32">
      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display text-soil sticky top-32">What makes it different</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8 text-lg text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">
            <p>In-person, I bring bodywork and every modality I've trained in into the same session. Breath and touch and sound, all at once. This is what clients tend to mean when they say they've done breathwork elsewhere and never felt anything like this.</p>
            <p>Online, I work with breath alongside specialised hypnotherapy. The depth is different but the work is still real, and for many clients being at home in their own space lets them go somewhere they wouldn't in a studio.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display text-soil sticky top-32">Formats</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <ul class="space-y-6 text-lg text-soil-muted">
              {[
                "Group sessions in-person — around three hours from start to finish",
                "Private sessions in-person — around three hours to begin with, building up to four as you go deeper",
                "Water breathwork — for clients who have done several land-based sessions",
                "Online sessions — private, with hypnotherapy integration",
                "Ten-session cards — for clients committed to the full arc"
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display text-soil sticky top-32">What clients come to breathwork for</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">Anxiety, depression, panic, shyness, low self-esteem, identity confusion, stuck grief, stored trauma, relationship patterns that keep repeating, chronic pain, asthma, skin conditions, burnout, and the feeling that they're not living anywhere near their full potential.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-12 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-secondary shadow-tactile">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display mb-6 text-soil">Important: who this isn't for</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-soil-muted leading-relaxed">Breathwork is powerful and there are some conditions where it isn't safe. Please don't book this work if you have cardiovascular problems, high blood pressure, a history of aneurysms, epilepsy, are on heavy medication, have active severe psychiatric symptoms, bipolar depression in an active phase, osteoporosis, recent surgery, glaucoma, are pregnant, are in active addiction, or are in a mental or spiritual emergency. Minimum age is eighteen.</p>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="therapy-note max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display italic text-soil mb-8 leading-relaxed">"What I experienced with Miro was beyond any description. Like I'm leaving my body and then coming back again but as a different person. It really feels like a rebirth."</p>
          <p class="font-hand text-4xl text-right text-primary">— Christopher</p>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal client:load>
        <div class="text-center bg-surface-container-low p-16 rounded-xl shadow-tactile">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display mb-8 text-soil">Ready to breathe?</h2>
          <a href="https://tidycal.com/miro-kloosterman/15-minute-meeting" class="btn-primary">Book a free discovery call</a>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
